%% Diagram: Client Credentials grant (machine-to-machine)
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client (Service)
    participant AuthZ as Authorization Server
    participant API as Resource Server

    Note over Client: No end user; client owns the credentials
    Client->>AuthZ: POST /token<br/>grant_type=client_credentials<br/>scope=...<br/>(client auth: secret / private_key_jwt / mTLS)
    AuthZ->>AuthZ: Authenticate client, evaluate scope
    AuthZ->>Client: access_token (no refresh_token, no id_token)
    Client->>API: Request + Authorization: Bearer / DPoP
    API->>AuthZ: (optional) introspect or verify JWT signature via JWKS
    API->>Client: Protected resource
